title: The Annihilation of John Fetterman
itunes:title: The Annihilation of John Fetterman
description:
Coming off the complete annihilation of John Fetterman in the Pennsylvania Senate Debate, Charlie unpacks some of Oz’s greatest wins alongside Fetterman’s ongoing and very painful trainwreck. Charlie investigates the change-of-mind many Pennsylvania citizens experienced last night playing back debate night reaction from PA voters. He also breaks major news LIVE that Darrell Brooks was found guilty on all accounts, and if you don’t know who that is, you need to listen.

Support the show: http://www.charliekirk.com/support
